Holonomic Robot Console
Copyright 2026 jarry050599

This product includes software developed for controlling an OminiBot HV
holonomic robot base over ROS 2.

The OminiBot HV v1.2 serial protocol implementation was reverse-engineered
and reimplemented from scratch; the brace-framed protocol it speaks is
referenced from the vendor driver published by iCShop / CIRCUSPi at
https://github.com/iCShopMgr/OminiBotHV

